<br>
However, as I'm in a raiding guild, levels means more powerfull spells, more resists (level based resists are VERY noticible), etc.<br>
<br>
So, my thoughts...<br>
<br>
Level to 60, then AAXP.<br>
<br>
or...<br>
<br>
Level to 51+, AAXP Run3.  You'll live longer, thus lose less XP.<br>
Level to 56, AAXP Regen3.  Helps with TRods.<br>
Level to 60, get safety XP margin, 100% AAXP.<br>
